{
  "stem": "6803.2",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was in a room with someone else that I knew before.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And all of a sudden my cousin walks in-- she lives now in Montreal, actually-- walks in.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I says, aren't you so-and-so?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She says, aren't you?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So therefore, we got together, and we stood together ever since, for a long-- for a few years.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then she got married, and I met my wife, and my first wife--",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My wife's name was Rosa, and she came also not far from--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She a survivor, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was a survivor.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we met, and we dated.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then in 1949, we decided we're going to go to Israel because her-- her father, as a matter of fact, survived.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was the oldest 55-year-old man in the whole district that he came back home from camp.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so therefore, we went to Israel, and we got married there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In '49.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was already Israel, yes, because in 1948, Israel was for-- was formed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we came to Israel in 1949, and we stayed there for 2 and 1/2 years.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I just couldn't stand the, uh-- the heat and all that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, I couldn't stand it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we tried to get out of there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then we got out to Canada, and we stayed in Canada for 12 and 1/2 years.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my daughter-- coming from Israel, coming to Canada, we had-- we had to stop in the consulate in Paris.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My older daughter was born in Paris.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Paris, In 1951 December 31.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we-- from there, we stayed another three weeks in Paris, and also the, uh, Rothschild Hospital.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were also very nice people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They treated my wife-- even though we didn't pay anything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't have any money actually.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
